The paper discusses a multidisciplinary approach to collaboration in the development of complex systems, which suggests a focus on software engineering (cs.SE) and systems and control (cs.SY). The use of simulation and co-simulation also suggests a potential fit with robotics (cs.RO), computer engineering (cs.CE), and emerging technologies (cs.ET).
